{
  "stem": "280.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were very fortunate because we were seven cousins in the same room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This cousin, whom I mentioned, a sister of hers, and other cousins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was even a  mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a few years younger than my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were first cousins, who survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Evidently, she looked young or she was lucky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She survived with her two daughters, and she was also in there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Today she is 95, and she's still mentally-- her-- her intellect is-- is fantastic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To talk with her is a pleasure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were assembling airplanes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were mostly screwing things in with long screwdrivers, you know, which-- which a woman's hands, fingers, were-- were easier to reach than a man's.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was operated by the Wehrmacht, not by the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were working about four or five girls under one master mechanic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I guess he was a mechanical engineer, who was also a Wehrmacht, and relatively a decent man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He sometimes brought us an apple, something to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had some conversations with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was somewhat of a human connection, a human touch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we more-- we had different food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had just, you know, in the morning some soup, and then we were given a piece of bread with a piece of margarine.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or they had those pieces of jelly like things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in the evening, we had something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the cook was a Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was-- it was very different than Auschwitz, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Auschwitz was a terrible-- Auschwitz was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was a-- a work camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in order to work, you had to eat something, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's where we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
